source.name: American Community Survey 5-year (2006-2010) SNAP/Foodstamp usage
source.description: A Bronx survey per census tract of foodstamp and SNAP (Supplemental Nutrition Assistance Program) usage for the years 2006-2010. There are many fields so refer to the attached ACS_10_5YR_S2201_Field_Dictionary.xlsx for field definitions, found in the "about" section of the dataset.
